00:05:49.960 --> 00:05:57.960
enjoyed that because you were meeting different people all the time. And we had a one time when Llyes Parker came,

00:05:58.960 --> 00:06:04.960
and Davy Crockett, the real one, came to Littlewoods, but we weren't allowed to say anything.

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:12.960
I'd seen him, but it was up to the other people to spot him and have a prize off him, you know, and that was exciting when that happened.

00:06:12.960 --> 00:06:20.960
But then we saw this old man used to come down on a Monday morning with one arm, as we thought,

00:06:20.960 --> 00:06:26.960
